   And I've tried everything.
     I've tried medication,
        and meditation,

58:05.783 --> 58:08.250
       and group therapy.
And you name it, I've tried it.

58:09.720 --> 58:14.056
     My prep for this night
       alone was Olympic.

58:14.258 --> 58:17.860
   Wait. You trained for me?

58:18.596 --> 58:19.661
      I guess I did, yeah.

58:24.735 --> 58:25.667
             Okay.

58:30.541 --> 58:31.707
        So, we stay in.

58:33.944 --> 58:36.912
   Wait, I tell you something
 incredibly screwy about myself

58:36.914 --> 58:39.648
